Title: HumanBreastCancerILC

Title: HumanCerebellum
Description: Visium spatial gene expression dataset of human cerebellum tissue (one section of 10 um thickness; whole transcriptome analysis + targeted neuroscience panel)

Title: HumanGlioblastoma
Description: Visium spatial gene expression dataset of human glioblastoma multiforme tissue (one section of 10 um thickness; whole transcriptome analysis + targeted pan-cancer panel)

Title: HumanHeart
Description: Visium spatial gene expression dataset of human heart tissue (one section of 10 um thickness)

Title: HumanLymphNode
Description: Visium spatial gene expression dataset or human lymph node tissue (one section of 10 um thickness)

Title: HumanOvarianCancer

Title: HumanSpinalCord
Description: Visium spatial gene expression dataset of human spinal cord tissue (one section of 10 um thickness; whole transcriptome analysis + targeted neuroscience panel)

Title: MouseBrainSagittalAnterior
